      <tuv lang="en-US">
        <seg>This report is provided “as is.” The Linux Foundation and its authors, contributors, and sponsors expressly disclaim any warranties (express, implied, or otherwise), including implied warranties of merchantability, noninfringement, fitness for a particular purpose, or title, related to this report.</seg>
